msgid ""
"A non-``NULL`` *bases* argument corresponds to the :c:data:`Py_tp_bases` "
"slot, and takes precedence over :c:data:`Py_tp_bases` and :c:data:"
"`Py_tp_bases` slots."
msgstr ""

#: ../../c-api/type.rst:785
msgid ""
"A non-``NULL`` *module* argument corresponds to the :c:macro:`Py_tp_module` "
"slot."
msgstr ""

#: ../../c-api/type.rst:790
msgid ""
"Note that this function does *not* fully match the behavior of calling :py:"
